title: 156: Super Bowl LI recap, coaching moves, RB prospects
itunes:title: 156: Super Bowl LI recap, coaching moves, RB prospects
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down Super Bowl LI, discussing Tom Brady's epic comeback and the Falcons blueprint for building a team. DJ and Buck also compare RB prospects Leonard Fournette and Dalvin Cook. The duo also give their takes on Atlanta's decision to bring in Steve Sarkisian as the team's offensive coordinator.
